TITLE: Registering Inbox Listener for Follow Activity with Fedify (TypeScript)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet registers an inbox listener for the 'Follow' activity using the Fedify framework. It expects a Federation instance and chains the 'setInboxListeners' and 'on' methods to handle incoming follow requests at specific inbox endpoints. Inputs include incoming ActivityPub follow activities; the output is logging the follower's information to the console. Dependencies: '@fedify/fedify'. Key parameters are inbox URI patterns and activity classes. This implementation does not yet respond with an Accept activity.
