TITLE: Installing Dependencies and Running Fedify Docs Development Server with Bun
DESCRIPTION: These commands install the necessary dependencies and start the development server for the Fedify documentation. They should be run in the docs/ directory after installing Bun.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fedify-dev/fedify/blob/main/docs/README.md#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
bun install
bun run dev
```

