TITLE: Building Fedify Project in Bash
DESCRIPTION: Commands to set up the development environment and generate code for the Fedify project using Deno.
SOURCE: https://github.com/fedify-dev/fedify/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md#2025-04-23_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
deno task codegen
code .
```
